          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Wholesale & Bulk Orders",
            "row_content": "<p>Interested in purchasing our products in bulk? We offer special pricing for coffee roasters, spice wholesalers, and food manufacturers. Contact our B2B team for custom quotes and samples.</p><p><a href=\"/pages/wholesale\">Learn more about wholesale →</a></p>",
